      <title>
        <ulink url="http://www.samba.org/samba/news/releases/3.6.0.html">Samba Team Releases Version 3.6</ulink>
      </title>
      <para>The Samba Team is proud to announce the release of Samba 3.6, a major new release of the award-winning Free Software file, print and authentication server suite for Microsoft Windows® clients.</para>
      <para><emphasis role="bold">The First Free Software SMB2 Server</emphasis></para>
      <para>Samba 3.6 includes the first Free Software implementation of Microsoft&apos;s new SMB2 file serving protocol. SMB2 within Samba is implemented with a brand new asynchronous server architecture, allowing Samba to display the performance enhancements SMB2 brings to Microsoft networking technology.</para>
      <para>Samba&apos;s new SMB2 server has been tested by major vendors and has been able to double the performance of some network applications when run in conjunction with Microsoft Windows 7® clients. (...)</para>
    </blockquote>
