        <ulink url="http://www.makeuseof.com/tag/kmail-kind-email-client-kde-linux/">MakeUseOf/Danny Stieben: KMail – A Different Kind Of Email Client For KDE</ulink>
      </title>
      <para>If you’ve been following the pretty intense battles between the many different browsers,
